name: Mothers of the Golden Swamp
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Mothers of the Golden Swamp are known to frequent Cinderkeep and consort with the mad wizard Zephyrial. Now finally living a life of leisure as their ‘investments’ grow their wealth beyond imagining, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
